An offence against any of the following provisions is a  regulatory
         offence:
         (a)      section 9A;
         (b)      section 24;
         (c)      section 39;
         (d)      section 45;
         (e)      section 56K(9);
         (f)      section 57;
         (g)      section 59(5).
